- Charley: Unless Davis
signs off on it.

00:10.770 --> 00:12.476
I think it's best
for both of us

00:12.510 --> 00:14.398
if we just keep things
professional.

00:14.440 --> 00:17.773
- Things didn't end right.
I wanna see you.
- Me, too, baby.

00:17.810 --> 00:20.278
Charley:
You have my son in custody.
This is your fault!

