- Do you want a receipt?
- No.

00:35.500 --> 00:36.626
Thank you.

00:38.170 --> 00:41.162
( music playing
on car stereo )

00:42.710 --> 00:44.701
What's going on, Darla?

00:44.740 --> 00:46.674
- Hey.
- Hey.

00:46.710 --> 00:48.268
What are you doing here?

00:48.310 --> 00:50.574
Oh, you know,
I just wanted to
see you, that's all.

00:50.610 --> 00:52.419
Come here.

00:52.450 --> 00:54.771
Hey!

00:54.820 --> 00:56.287
Hi.

00:56.320 --> 00:58.618
Pop's taking me out
on an errand, Mama.

00:58.650 --> 01:01.551
What?
That sounds
like a special day.

01:01.590 --> 01:03.285
Wanna come with us?

01:03.330 --> 01:05.548
Can't. Wish I could.
Working.

01:05.590 --> 01:07.319
I got you something.

01:07.360 --> 01:09.419
Beignets
and that caf au lait.

01:09.470 --> 01:12.166
- That's the thing
you like, right?
- Yes.

01:12.200 --> 01:15.135
- Thank you.
- Mm-hmm.

01:15.170 --> 01:17.138
( clears throat )

01:17.170 --> 01:19.707
So, I wanted to know
about us, uh...

01:19.740 --> 01:22.402
taking it slow and all.

01:22.450 --> 01:24.441
But I was hoping I could
take you out tonight.

01:24.480 --> 01:25.447
( laughs )

01:25.480 --> 01:26.777
- On a date.
' ( gasps )

01:26.820 --> 01:28.708
A real date.

01:30.150 --> 01:31.242
A proper date.

01:31.290 --> 01:34.111
( horn honks )

01:34.160 --> 01:35.582
You better
get gomg.

01:35.620 --> 01:36.826
No.

01:36.860 --> 01:39.499
Not till I get my answer.

01:41.230 --> 01:44.165
Is that a yes?

01:44.200 --> 01:45.394
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

01:45.430 --> 01:47.739
- You heard that, Blue?
- Yep.

01:47.770 --> 01:49.761
- Bye, my loves.
- Bye.

